Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.29,0:22:43.54,ed,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}ワープでループなこの想いは
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.57,0:22:49.31,ed,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}何もかもを巻き込んだ想像で遊ぼう
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.54,0:22:52.02,ed,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}アル晴レタ日ノ事
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.27,0:22:54.67,ed,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}魔法以上のユカイが
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.71,0:22:59.98,ed,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}限りなく降りそそぐ　不可能じゃないわ
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.66,0:23:05.83,ed,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}明日また会うとき　笑いながらハミング
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.97,0:23:08.95,ed,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}嬉しさを集めよう
Dialogue: 0,0:23:09.07,0:23:11.48,ed,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}カンタンなんだよ　こ{\fe134\fn方正准圆简体\fs23}·{\r}ん{\fe134\fn方正准圆_GBK\fs23}·{\r}な{\fe134\fn方正准圆_GBK\fs23}·{\r}の
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.56,0:23:16.08,ed,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}追いかけてね　つかまえてみて
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.24,0:23:20.02,ed,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}大きな夢＆夢　スキでしょう？
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.47,0:22:33.03,edzw,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}就像是那地球仪上各种谜团　都一一解说开来
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.17,0:22:36.74,edzw,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}大家就能随心所欲地到处旅行
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.86,0:22:39.22,edzw,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}想一直到时间尽头Boooon!!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.29,0:22:43.54,edzw,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}那想法像变成圆圈一样
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.57,0:22:49.31,edzw,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}不管什么都要把这一切卷进幻想里面去玩吧
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.54,0:22:52.02,edzw,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}在那晴空之下的故事
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.27,0:22:54.67,edzw,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}是比魔法还更加愉快的
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.71,0:22:59.98,edzw,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}永无尽头地倾注到世界　一切皆有可能呢
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.66,0:23:05.83,edzw,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}明天再与你见面之时　带着灿烂笑容轻松哼唱
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.97,0:23:08.95,edzw,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}把那些喜悦收集起来吧
Dialogue: 0,0:23:09.07,0:23:11.48,edzw,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}这些其实都非常　简·单·容·易
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.56,0:23:16.08,edzw,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}赶快追上去吧　试着抓住它吧
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.24,0:23:20.02,edzw,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}那雄伟的梦想＆梦想　你喜欢吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.23,0:01:30.27,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,答えはいつも私の胸に...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.99,0:01:46.14,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,なんでだろ　あなたを選んだ私です
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.45,0:01:52.47,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,もうとまらない　運命様から決められたけど
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.52,0:01:58.71,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I believe　真似だけじゃつまらないの
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.81,0:02:01.04,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You'll be right！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.39,0:02:07.49,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,感じるまま感じることだけをするよ
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.62,0:02:14.34,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,冒険でしょでしょ！ホントが嘘に変わる世界で
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.37,0:02:21.19,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夢があるから強くなるのよ　誰の為じゃない
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.55,0:02:24.56,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一緒に来てくださいっ
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.82,0:02:30.27,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,どこまでも自由な私を見てよね
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.28,0:02:35.66,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明日過去になった今日のいまが奇跡
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.06,0:02:42.13,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,つかもう未来を
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.37,0:02:47.76,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I believe you...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.23,0:01:30.27,OP中文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这份答案一直存在于我的内心里...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.99,0:01:46.14,OP中文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,究竟为什么　选择你的居然会是区区的我呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.45,0:01:52.47,OP中文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已不能停步　虽然能让高贵的命运来决定一切
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.52,0:01:58.71,OP中文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I believe　单纯的模仿一定十分无聊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.81,0:02:01.04,OP中文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You'll be right！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.39,0:02:07.49,OP中文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,照着感觉走　只去做那感觉到的事情吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.62,0:02:14.34,OP中文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,冒险对吧对吧！在真实变成了谎言的世界之中
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.37,0:02:21.19,OP中文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,若能够拥有梦想　就可以收获坚强　并不是为了谁而去
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.55,0:02:24.56,OP中文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就请你与我一起来
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.82,0:02:30.27,OP中文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而看着这个无论何处都会是自由的我啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.28,0:02:35.66,OP中文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在明天变成过去之前将此日此时的那奇迹
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.06,0:02:42.13,OP中文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,牢牢抓住面向未来
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.37,0:02:47.76,OP中文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I believe you...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.66,0:00:19.53,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我泡了茶
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.01,0:00:20.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请用
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.97,0:00:22.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.93,0:00:31.73,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很好喝呢
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.66,0:00:35.54,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请用
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.77,0:00:37.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢你  朝比奈同学
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.49,0:00:42.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,五月份春日建立SOS团之后光阴飞逝
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.28,0:00:43.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在已经是六月了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.79,0:00:46.31,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其实在这段时间里面
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.70,0:00:50.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我已经被卷入了很多将我的世界观完全推翻的事件
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.50,0:00:51.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过那些先放在一边
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.19,0:00:53.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这次是这样一个故事
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.27,0:00:57.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,各位！我们要参加棒球大赛！
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.53,0:00:59.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,从那天起直到今天
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.30,0:01:02.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都没有发生什么值得一提的事件
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.64,0:01:05.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一直都在享受着悠闲的平静与无聊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.30,0:01:08.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是看来那段日子也只是转瞬即逝而已
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.01,0:01:09.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,至于为什么
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.94,0:01:13.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要这家伙一旦这样一脸高兴地笑着
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.48,0:01:16.43,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不知道为什么我就会变成疲劳的线操人偶
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.45,0:02:55.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你说要参加什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.40,0:02:56.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.05,0:03:02.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第九届室内业余棒球大赛
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.93,0:03:06.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么  是谁要去参加这个草地棒球赛？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.93,0:03:06.58,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,（草地棒球：外行人参加的以尽兴为目的的棒球比赛）
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.74,0:03:08.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,当然是我们了！这还用问？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.94,0:03:12.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你所谓的「我们」是不是把我们几个也算进去了？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.05,0:03:13.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们还需要再找4个人吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.74,0:03:18.27,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和平时一样  是个不把对自己的想法有异议的话听进耳朵的家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.79,0:03:20.79,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你懂棒球的规则吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.90,0:03:22.36,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这我当然知道了啦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.94,0:03:25.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好歹我也是尝试参加过棒球社的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.16,0:03:26.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,多少懂一点
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.89,0:03:29.36,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然因为一点意思都没有所以很快就回家了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.68,0:03:33.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么我们为什么还非要参加\N这种「一点意思都没有」的棒球大赛？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.93,0:03:37.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是让全天下知道我们存在的大好机会啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.49,0:03:39.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果能在比赛中获胜的话
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.21,0:03:43.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也许SOS团的名号能够一举独步天下呢！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.36,0:03:44.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,机会难得啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.79,0:03:46.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么样  是个好主意吧  实玖瑠
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.22,0:03:48.72,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦？可  可是…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.77,0:03:50.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯？棒球很不错吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.94,0:03:53.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我先说清楚  我们的目标是最终胜利！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.43,0:03:57.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一场比赛都不许输！因为我最讨厌失败了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.19,0:04:00.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明白了吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.51,0:04:02.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有何不可呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.83,0:04:04.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别这么干脆地就答应了！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.06,0:04:07.56,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,偶尔也应该提出一点反驳意见吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.01,0:04:10.54,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比起到处乱转去寻找外星人或者UMA
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.01,0:04:10.54,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,（UMA：Unidentified Mysterious Animals，未知生物）
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.78,0:04:12.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我认为这个活动要健康得多呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.48,0:04:16.43,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么  这个比赛什么时候开始？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.61,0:04:17.57,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个星期天
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.72,0:04:18.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那不就是后天吗！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.86,0:04:20.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再怎么说时间也太紧了吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.48,0:04:22.27,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是我已经报名了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.69,0:04:23.72,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  你放心
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.03,0:04:26.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,队伍名称我已经报好是「SOS团」了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.94,0:04:28.57,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这里我可是决不会出错的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.95,0:04:33.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其他的4个队员你打算从哪里挖啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.44,0:04:36.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要随便逮几个在那些到处闲晃的人不就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.95,0:04:38.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是认真这么说的么…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.28,0:04:41.63,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道了  你先别轻举妄动
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.44,0:04:45.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总之…谷口和国木田好像满闲的…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.66,0:04:46.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那些也行
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.88,0:04:49.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她用「那些」来称呼同班同学
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.75,0:04:52.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯…还剩下两个人吗…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.92,0:04:56.03,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请问…如果我的朋友也可以的话…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.09,0:04:56.79,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就也算上那个
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.86,0:04:58.03,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像什么人都可以啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.21,0:04:59.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯？等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.27,0:05:00.61,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,朝比奈学姐的朋友？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.91,0:05:02.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我有点放心不下了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.35,0:05:03.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是什么「时候」  什么「地方」交的朋友啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.96,0:05:05.73,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  没关系的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.82,0:05:07.29,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是在这个时间…啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.02,0:05:10.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在班上认识的朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.68,0:05:12.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么我也来推荐一个人吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.38,0:05:15.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,实际上  我认识的一个人对我们的事很感兴趣…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.93,0:05:17.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最后的人选由我来想办法
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.82,0:05:20.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,既然决定好了就马上来特训吧！特训！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.57,0:05:22.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,特训？现在就开始？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.79,0:05:23.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.58,0:05:24.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在哪里啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.55,0:05:25.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那里
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.41,0:05:33.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,于是我们就要去参加棒球比赛了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.53,0:05:34.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.92,0:05:36.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个答案很简单
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.17,0:05:39.43,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也就是  只不过是因为春日她…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.70,0:05:41.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有点烦闷而已
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.25,0:05:44.13,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂  打扰一下
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.40,0:05:45.79,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把这个地方借给我们吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.96,0:05:47.53,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还有棒球用具也是
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.63,0:05:49.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊？你说什么啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.33,0:05:52.61,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为我们必须要赶快进行棒球训练嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.82,0:05:53.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们比较碍事  闪开吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.01,0:05:55.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们怎么可能答应啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.54,0:05:56.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有什么关系嘛！只借一阵子就好
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.03,0:05:58.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对吧  实玖瑠
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.96,0:06:03.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.74,0:06:06.09,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是容易被看穿的青春时期
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.78,0:06:09.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么先打个一千棒！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.03,0:06:10.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要去了！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.23,0:06:21.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这球上可寄托了SOS团的未来！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.76,0:06:23.13,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,给我好好接住！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.52,0:06:27.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第一次听说我们的未来原来是寄托在这么小的一个球上
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.23,0:06:37.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再来一次！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.31,0:06:39.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,实玖瑠  要来了哦～
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.25,0:06:44.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好痛哦…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.77,0:06:50.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没事吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.12,0:06:51.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还站得起来吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.64,0:06:54.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿虚  不行
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.76,0:06:57.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果和我感情这么好的话  又会…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.22,0:07:01.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂！阿虚！实玖瑠！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.19,0:07:02.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,给我回来！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.84,0:07:03.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们受伤退场！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.87,0:07:05.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,算了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.08,0:07:08.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下面棒球社的给我补上去
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.21,0:07:09.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么我们要…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.46,0:07:17.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好  今天就到此为止吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.51,0:07:21.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是令人吃惊啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.93,0:07:24.47,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的正好是打了一千棒呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.63,0:07:27.57,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,倒是连这个都能数得一清二楚的你比较令我吃惊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.76,0:07:29.53,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  长门
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.08,0:07:33.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比赛当天能不能让老天下场雨？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.52,0:07:35.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是能让比赛中止的那种大雨
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.88,0:07:36.81,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是不能
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.25,0:07:38.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是不推荐
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.01,0:07:39.53,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.61,0:07:42.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对局部性的环境资料进行篡改
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.12,0:07:45.74,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有对行星生态系统造成后遗症的可能性
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.05,0:07:47.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,后遗症是…大约多久以后会发作？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.81,0:07:49.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,几百年到一万年
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.08,0:07:53.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那还是别这么做比较好了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.44,0:07:55.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.53,0:08:02.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就这样  比赛当天来临了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.84,0:08:05.27,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,…其实不来临也没什么问题的说…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.45,0:08:09.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你就是阿虚？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.01,0:08:12.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我经常听实玖瑠提起你呢！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.39,0:08:13.29,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.67,0:08:14.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喔…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.88,0:08:17.57,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个  这位是我的朋友鹤屋…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.74,0:08:19.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是谷口  请多多关照
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.69,0:08:21.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是国木田
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.83,0:08:24.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀～阿虚是我的好朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.17,0:08:25.36,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他的请求我实在没办法拒绝啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.60,0:08:26.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀哎呀
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.60,0:08:27.65,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}是谷口和国木田对吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.96,0:08:29.05,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}我记住了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.67,0:08:30.85,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}这是我们的光荣
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.14,0:08:28.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿虚
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.62,0:08:30.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,过来一下
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.10,0:08:34.44,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在想什么啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.69,0:08:36.73,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那种家伙你也想让她上场打球？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.11,0:08:38.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说「那种家伙」也太失礼了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.79,0:08:40.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么说可也是我的妹妹哦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.77,0:08:44.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她自我介绍说是「小学五年级生  现在10岁」哦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.51,0:08:47.91,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是个坦率到无法联想到是你妹妹一般的好孩子呢！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.36,0:08:52.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过重点在于我们参加的可是一般年龄层的棒球赛！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.43,0:08:53.81,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是青少年级的啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.05,0:08:55.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道啊春日小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.71,0:08:57.98,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以才会把妹妹带来啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.27,0:08:59.91,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然说本来就不可能打赢的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.11,0:09:01.54,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过这可是春日搞出来的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.69,0:09:03.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果一不小心真的最终胜出了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.39,0:09:05.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一定会变成超级麻烦的事情的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.41,0:09:07.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果混一个小学五年级生进去的话
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.39,0:09:09.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样能赢才奇怪呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.18,0:09:12.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,算了  没关系
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.33,0:09:13.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正好稍微放一下水
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.13,0:09:16.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果赢得太狠也就太不给对手面子了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.27,0:09:17.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像她还真的想要打赢啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.77,0:09:23.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,倒是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.03,0:09:25.98,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还没有决定打击顺序和守备位置呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.13,0:09:26.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么办？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.87,0:09:28.31,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我已经想好了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.92,0:09:31.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,用这个来决定！没有意见了吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.49,0:09:33.93,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有打击的顺序和防守的位置两种
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.10,0:09:36.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,另外我是投手和一棒
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.95,0:09:39.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你想好的只有决定的方法吗…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.77,0:09:41.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,干什么  你有什么不满意的吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.00,0:09:43.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这可是民主的方法啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.81,0:09:46.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,古希腊可是还用抽签来选政治家呢！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.87,0:09:51.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别把古希腊的政治制度\N和现代日本的草地棒球打击顺序混为一谈好不好
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.72,0:09:53.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且只有你可以按照兴趣来选择
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.88,0:09:55.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,算什么民主啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.30,0:09:57.00,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,名字      守备位置\N一棒  凉宫春日  投手
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.10,0:09:57.80,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,二棒  实玖瑠    右外野\N三棒  有希      中间手
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.90,0:09:58.60,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,四棒  阿虚      二垒手\N五棒  虚妹      左外野
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.70,0:09:59.40,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,六棒  古泉      捕手\N七棒  国木田    一垒手
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.50,0:10:00.20,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,八棒  鹤屋      三垒手\N九棒  谷口      游击手
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.10,0:09:56.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,算了  也好
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.15,0:09:58.71,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看起来能够更快地回去了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.11,0:10:00.53,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为刚刚听说了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.81,0:10:03.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第一场的对手是叫做「上上原海盗」的大学生球队
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.08,0:10:06.31,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是本届大赛的种子队伍之一
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.67,0:10:09.13,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为只要得分相差10分就会提前结束比赛
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.40,0:10:13.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在就开始准备回家应该也不算早了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.83,0:10:16.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22}Play Ball！{\r}\N比赛开始！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.91,0:10:32.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他投的球完全没什么好怕的！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.12,0:10:34.72,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家都跟上来吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.55,0:10:39.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请多指教…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.24,0:10:40.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22}Strike！{\r}\N好球！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.23,0:10:44.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你这厮对着朝比奈学姐投得是什么该死的球！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.38,0:10:45.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你给我打到她身上一个看看
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.27,0:10:46.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我马上就去跟你们群殴！把这里变成群殴狂欢！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.05,0:10:49.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22}Strike！{\r}\N好球！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.84,0:10:50.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,实玖瑠！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.24,0:10:53.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,使劲打啊！使劲！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.49,0:10:55.61,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22}Struck Out！{\r}\N三振出局！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.96,0:10:59.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂！为什么不挥棒啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.02,0:11:00.72,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22}Strike！{\r}\N好球！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.96,0:11:01.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22}Strike！{\r}\N好球！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.75,0:11:03.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22}Struck Out！{\r}\N三振出局！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.57,0:11:06.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有希！如果不挥棒的话不是就更不会打中了吗！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.95,0:11:10.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿虚  你一定要打中啊！你可是四棒！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.95,0:11:10.17,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,（一般四棒的位置会安排打击力最强的队员，称之为强打或强棒）
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.59,0:11:13.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在期待我这个抽签决定的四棒做些什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.15,0:11:16.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22}Strike！{\r}\N好球！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.65,0:11:18.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,春日是面对这种球打出长打的吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.51,0:11:20.36,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22}Strike！{\r}\N好球！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.44,0:11:29.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22}Struck Out！{\r}\N三振出局！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.23,0:11:32.43,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,白痴！你在做什么啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.74,0:11:32.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,遗憾！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.26,0:11:36.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,严防死守吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.97,0:11:38.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好——！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.56,0:11:42.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22}Play！{\r}\N比赛继续！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.67,0:11:45.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22}Strike！{\r}\N好球！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.77,0:11:49.53,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22}Strike！{\r}\N好球！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.77,0:11:52.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22}Struck Out！{\r}\N三振出局！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.37,0:11:53.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Nice pitch!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.86,0:11:55.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,游刃有余啦～
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.39,0:12:02.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22}Foul ball！{\r}\N界外球！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.69,0:12:20.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为她只会冲着好球区投直球而已
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.63,0:12:22.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一旦被人看出来当然会被打中吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.13,0:12:27.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且我们守备的漏洞比热带大草原上蚁巢的还要多
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.39,0:12:28.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,竹筐一样！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.86,0:12:31.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这一回合总算是把失分控制在2分
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.31,0:12:35.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一定是因为对方的胜利女神来晚了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.66,0:12:38.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,星期天谁都希望休息一下嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.69,0:12:41.73,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接下来  第二轮的攻势也是毫无悬念地结束了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.69,0:12:39.32,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}{\fs17}Struck Out！{\r}\N三振出局！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.42,0:12:39.97,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}{\fs17}Struck Out！{\r}\N三振出局！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.10,0:12:40.77,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}{\fs17}Struck Out！{\r}\N三振出局！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.14,0:12:44.94,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,之后又很干脆地被对方拿下了几分
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.43,0:12:47.71,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看来下一回合就可以结束了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.58,0:12:51.53,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22}Out！{\r}\N出局！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.02,0:12:55.98,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太难了吧  光是让球棒打到球就用尽全力了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.28,0:12:59.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然还是需要那个吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.01,0:13:02.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22}　Time{\r}\N先暂停
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.06,0:13:05.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦？等  等一下…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.18,0:13:08.74,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,凉宫同学…不  不要啊——
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.86,0:13:11.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了！快点给我脱好换衣服！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.86,0:13:17.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,实玖瑠  可以拍下来吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.86,0:13:16.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好合适哦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.24,0:13:20.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是不是绑个马尾比较好啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.12,0:13:26.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了  来加油吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.80,0:13:28.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个  要怎么做呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.75,0:13:30.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是这么做～
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.20,0:13:32.61,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来  大声加油吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.70,0:13:35.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,各  各位！请打中吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.61,0:13:37.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,求你们了  加油吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.11,0:13:39.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好的～包在我身上！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.16,0:13:41.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22}Struck Out！{\r}\N三振出局！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.41,0:13:42.74,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这种球果然还是打不到啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.33,0:13:45.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,算了  反正也没指望你
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.53,0:14:01.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,安全上垒！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.55,0:14:04.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,实玖瑠！这次一定要打中哦！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.64,0:14:05.50,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}上吧！实玖瑠！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.43,0:14:05.80,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}朝比奈学姐！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.41,0:14:10.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22}Strike！{\r}\N好球！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.24,0:14:12.57,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,实玖瑠！这个啊  用这个！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.36,0:14:14.54,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她在搞什么啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.19,0:14:18.53,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难道这样能让对方投手的MP减少吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.09,0:14:21.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看来好像是在打暗号呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.10,0:14:23.61,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们决定过什么暗号吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.85,0:14:24.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没用
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.03,0:14:28.93,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是我想那大概是叫她用抢分战术吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.03,0:14:28.93,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,（抢分战术：跑者在三垒时，打击手使用牺牲打令跑者得以回本垒的战术）
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.25,0:14:31.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,二人出局还打抢分战术的暗号？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.54,0:14:36.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算是那个永世教练也会用更常识性的战术吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.54,0:14:36.04,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,（永世教练：指巨人队的长岛教练，\N巨人队时代教练都由长岛家的人担任而得名。被很多球迷厌恶）
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.69,0:14:41.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也许是发现了朝比奈打中球的几率基本上是零
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.71,0:14:43.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,该不会是因此做出意义不明的暗号
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.88,0:14:45.31,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,故意让对方看透
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.64,0:14:48.63,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也许会令内野手出现失误
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.97,0:14:55.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,或是希望朝比奈同学用牺牲打打中球的话也能有办法
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.48,0:14:57.09,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然完全被人家看透了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.75,0:14:59.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22}Strike！{\r}\N好球！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.42,0:15:01.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22}Struck Out！{\r}\N三振出局！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.69,0:15:03.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,实玖瑠  你给我过来
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.65,0:15:04.81,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然后咬紧牙关！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.58,0:15:06.53,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是惩罚  惩罚！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.82,0:15:09.72,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要让大家看看你这张可笑的脸！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.02,0:15:11.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.79,0:15:12.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是白痴吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.16,0:15:16.57,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是打出莫名其妙暗号的你不好
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.87,0:15:19.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,自己去盗本垒不好吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.70,0:15:30.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大事不好了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.73,0:15:32.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我虽然不想听  不过你姑且说说看吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.49,0:15:35.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一个前所未有的大规模封闭空间开始产生了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.21,0:15:38.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且还正在以非常快的速度扩大着
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.41,0:15:43.54,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要凉宫同学的心情不恢复  它就会持续扩大
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.91,0:15:45.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「那个」也就会继续大肆破坏
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.90,0:15:46.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是这样了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.02,0:15:48.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是因为打输了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.21,0:15:51.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是个不懂事的小鬼！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.29,0:15:52.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然你说得好像是别人的事情一样
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.07,0:15:56.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过这和你也有很大的关系哦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.33,0:15:59.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为决定打击顺序的时候我们不是抽签了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.43,0:16:03.09,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而作为结果  你是四棒
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.24,0:16:04.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我可不觉得高兴
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.70,0:16:06.43,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是因为凉宫同学这样希望
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.55,0:16:08.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以你才成为了第四棒打击手
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.65,0:16:09.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这并非偶然
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.79,0:16:14.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且  你完全没有起到四棒的作用
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.13,0:16:15.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以她失望了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.76,0:16:16.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真抱歉啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.02,0:16:21.61,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总之  这一回合尽全力令比赛不要提前结束吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.00,0:16:24.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果现在比赛结束了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.08,0:16:26.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就等同于世界末日来临
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.09,0:16:28.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂！要开始了！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.14,0:16:30.74,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,无论如何  都要把失分控制在两分以内
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.84,0:16:38.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,两人出局  跑者在一  二垒
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.79,0:16:40.19,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在零对九
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.48,0:16:42.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还有一分就会强制结束比赛吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.48,0:16:47.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来这边了！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.25,0:16:50.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要赶上啊  要赶上啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.75,0:16:53.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  好厉害哦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.65,0:16:55.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Nice Play！干得不错嘛！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.39,0:16:56.79,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不愧是我的好友！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.82,0:17:03.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,继续刚才的话题
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.60,0:17:04.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的脸凑得太近了  什么事啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.15,0:17:08.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你上次和凉宫同学一起到那个世界去的时候
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.05,0:17:10.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是怎么回来的？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.74,0:17:12.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别让我想起那件事来！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.65,0:17:16.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果用那一招的话  也许又能够顺利解决了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.38,0:17:17.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我拒绝
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.37,0:17:18.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想也是这样
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.22,0:17:21.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么就用些能够确保胜利的方法吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.75,0:17:25.93,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们和她之间的利害关系应该也是一致的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.70,0:17:31.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,长门同学终于也…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.13,0:17:33.79,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她做了什么吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.18,0:17:35.91,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她好像在咏唱咒文
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.16,0:17:38.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咒文？那是什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.98,0:17:41.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯…这是禁止谈论的事项
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.07,0:17:44.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咒文吗…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.96,0:18:00.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好厉害啊！你怎么有这么大的力气？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.44,0:18:03.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个  对属性信息作了能力提升改写
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.33,0:18:03.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.11,0:18:05.31,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,制导模式
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.91,0:18:08.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,飞得好远！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.28,0:18:11.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原来如此  制导模式啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.36,0:18:14.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂喂  乱来也要有点限度嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.66,0:18:25.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不管怎么说  再这样下去就糟糕了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.88,0:18:27.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在各种意义上…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.83,0:18:29.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已经足够了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.15,0:18:31.79,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.41,0:18:32.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22}Strike！{\r}\N好球！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.98,0:18:33.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22}Strike！{\r}\N好球！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.41,0:18:33.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22}Strike！{\r}\N好球！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.47,0:18:38.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,刚才忘记说了  第一场比赛时间限制为90分钟
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.88,0:18:40.63,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以已经没有下一回合了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.92,0:18:43.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要守住这一回合  我们就获胜了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.10,0:18:45.47,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以吗？就这样获胜
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.05,0:18:47.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是不获胜不行吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.96,0:18:52.79,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,多亏如此  封闭空间的扩大速度似乎已经降下来了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.23,0:18:56.29,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过如果在这里被对方逆转局势的话可就再见滑铁卢了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.49,0:19:00.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过猜那个时候春日心情如何也没有意义了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.47,0:19:01.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以我有个提议
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.95,0:19:04.72,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你说真的吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.80,0:19:05.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,非常当真
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.69,0:19:08.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想要把这一回合的失分控制在最低
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.99,0:19:10.53,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就只有这个方法了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.20,0:19:12.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀哎呀
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.71,0:19:17.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22}Ball！{\r}\N坏球！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.81,0:19:21.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂！你给我好好投！难得我和你交换位置
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.07,0:19:22.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果输了的话就罚你请所有人吃饭！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.24,0:19:24.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.78,0:19:28.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不管怎么说  我投的球可是负担着全世界的命运啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.66,0:19:30.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,…这个世界还真是不值钱啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.31,0:19:36.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22}Strike！{\r}\N好球！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.29,0:19:39.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,由于这Mysterious Ball（命名：我）的缘故
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.64,0:19:41.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看来世界不需要被毁灭了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.71,0:19:45.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22}S…Strike two！{\r}\N两…两好球！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.82,0:19:46.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22}Struck Out！{\r}\N三振出局！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.03,0:19:51.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接下来的打击手也很无聊地被三球三振了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.30,0:19:50.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22}Struck Out！{\r}\N三振出局！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.49,0:19:53.31,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,恐怕会已经成为最后的打击手的那个人
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.38,0:19:54.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在也已经两好球了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.68,0:19:54.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22}Strike two！{\r}\N两好球！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.77,0:19:57.32,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿虚  还有一球  决出胜负吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.47,0:19:59.73,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算你不说这球也会决定胜负吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.12,0:20:02.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉了  上上原海盗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.86,0:20:05.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,侥幸！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.77,0:20:06.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要不死三振了！长门！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.77,0:20:08.55,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,（不死三振：在一垒无人情况下，\N捕手未能接到应该能将打击手三振的球时，打击手安全冲上一垒）
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.34,0:20:08.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去捡起球来投过去！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.06,0:20:13.31,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快点啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.96,0:20:18.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,二垒！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.99,0:20:18.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这边这边！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.00,0:20:19.43,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.55,0:20:19.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呀？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.95,0:20:20.29,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.52,0:20:24.71,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是非常抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.16,0:20:28.32,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们这一群人稍微有点超乎常理
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.73,0:20:30.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22}Ga…game and set！{\r}\N比…比赛结束！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.73,0:20:30.26,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,（日文的省略读法读作「Game set」）
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.05,0:20:34.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然由于长门的作弊式魔法我们打赢了这一场…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.42,0:20:37.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第二场要怎么办？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.43,0:20:40.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果就这样继续打第二场的话
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.47,0:20:42.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有些对不起上上原海盗  而且…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.46,0:20:47.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其实我也差不多该去给「同伴」们帮忙了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.87,0:20:49.44,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样的话人数也不够了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.94,0:20:50.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,弃权吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.92,0:20:51.95,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样比较好呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.43,0:20:55.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看来不能让凉宫同学闲下来呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.24,0:20:58.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这就作为今后的课题吧  有研究的价值
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.86,0:21:01.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你也玩够了吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.69,0:21:03.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,古泉说有急事要回去了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.11,0:21:07.54,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的腿和手臂也都累得动不了了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.43,0:21:15.94,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,既然你觉得可以  那就这样吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.42,0:21:17.54,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也有些饿了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.97,0:21:19.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去吃午饭吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.91,0:21:20.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好的好的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.18,0:21:23.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的太感谢你了！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.53,0:21:24.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哪里哪里
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.79,0:21:25.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么  我先告辞了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.65,0:21:27.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.22,0:21:29.44,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,关于你这根球棒…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.33,0:21:34.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我自己都没有注意到过呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.70,0:21:36.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原来我有打棒球的天分啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.73,0:21:36.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你就是长门有希？听实玖瑠她经常提到你呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.38,0:21:39.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家尽量多吃点吧  今天阿虚请客～
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.66,0:21:41.57,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,算了  也好
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.04,0:21:44.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,反正我口袋里也有一笔临时收入了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.09,0:21:47.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我衷心期盼上上原海盗队能拿下傲人战绩
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.04,0:21:54.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,佐生！好好打！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.52,0:22:01.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉来迟啦～！
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.64,0:22:03.63,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂  这次参加哪个好？
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.86,0:22:06.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,足球和美式橄榄球都是多少人参加的运动？
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.23,0:22:09.43,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只用之前的那些人够吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.77,0:22:11.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一面看着春日最美丽的笑容
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.39,0:22:15.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我开始考虑哪个是人数最少的运动
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.28,0:22:18.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,美式橄榄球…不！去给我打门球吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.28,0:22:18.80,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,（一种只需要5个人的球类运动）
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.96,0:00:15.93,neta,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,[三种不同的茶杯…这个细节我都不记得了OTL]
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.49,0:00:43.74,neta,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,[不带眼镜的长门大明神啊～！（大心）]
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.79,0:00:50.18,neta,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,[「…而现在那套女仆装已经用衣架挂起来，吊在社团活动室的角落了」]
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.45,0:02:56.50,neta,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,[「因为没有人有任何反应，所以一如往常还是由我勉为其难地反问春日。\N为什么大家老是把我当成和春日沟通的管道？\N再没有任何事情比这个任务更让我伤脑筋的了」]
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.05,0:03:02.37,neta,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,[「主办单位是市公所，似乎是历史悠久、每年都会举办的活动」]
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.88,0:04:29.88,neta,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,[「我全身一阵虚脱」]
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.28,0:04:45.42,neta,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,[「而且春日会锁定的人除了一个例外，向来都不是普通人。\N那个极少数的例外就是我。而我并不打算再认识更多来历不明的人了。」]
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.38,0:04:49.40,neta,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,[（春日：）「总比没有好」]
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.70,0:05:41.06,neta,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,[这里特别配合台版小说翻译成“烦闷”…不过其实还是无聊比较准确OTL]
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.93,0:06:39.05,neta,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,[「你好歹也多动一点吧。还是我该夸奖你动态视力极佳呢？」]
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.68,0:06:44.85,neta,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,[「…一个不规则弹跳的硬球掠过我的手套，\N穿过我的胯下，直接命中了朝比奈的膝盖。」]
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.08,0:06:59.09,neta,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,[「又会怎样？我耸耸肩。」]
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.99,0:07:51.64,neta,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,[「好久远的未来啊」]
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.84,0:08:05.27,neta,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,[等过了暑假保准你不会再这么说。]
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.79,0:08:40.50,neta,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,[通称：虚妹]
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.81,0:10:03.82,neta,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,[上上原海盗是台版小说的翻译，\N原文“上ヶ原パイレーツ”，感觉译作“上原海盗”就可以了…]
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.12,0:10:35.41,neta,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,[「春日气势汹汹地大叫。可是，她这种做法完全是反效果。」]
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.64,0:10:37.21,neta,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,[「因为这么一来，对方选手对女生手下留情的心情早就消失得无影无踪了」]
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.27,0:10:46.87,neta,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,[原文“乱闘パーティー”…难道是在EG“乱○派对”？！]
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.21,0:11:14.67,neta,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,[「…事实上，我感觉投手投出球的那一刹那，球就已经进入捕手的手套里了。」]
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.44,0:11:29.84,neta,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,[「哇！球转弯了。这就是所谓的曲球吗？」]
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.43,0:12:17.35,neta,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,[「春日带着仿佛被伊阿宋背叛的美狄亚公主般的眼神，\N看着在内也跑了一圈的对方第三棒打击手」\N（和动画略有不同）]
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.26,0:13:26.50,neta,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,[「（春日）发现我投注过去的视线之后，\N她把嘴巴嘟得像鸭子一样尖，放弃弄头发了。」]
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.36,0:15:26.30,neta,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,[“脑”]
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.08,0:16:26.08,neta,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,[「古泉带着与充满危机感的说话内容完全不搭调的表情说着」]
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.65,0:17:16.28,neta,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,[苦啊！苦啊！]
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.36,0:17:47.72,neta,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,[「SELECT serial code FROM database WHERE code data ORDER BY 攻击性信息战斗 HAVING terminate mode。\Npersonal name 朝仓凉子，判断为敌性。\N解除该对象的有机信息连接。」]
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.85,0:17:48.77,neta,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,[按原文看来貌似长门是在对某“主机”下达指令，\N（如上我所写的）大写的部分是命令格式，小写和中文部分是具体参数吧…]
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.66,0:18:25.62,neta,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,[「…因为我觉得对方选手的视线不在我们这些选手身上，\N反倒全集中在这支球棒上了。…」]
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.88,0:18:27.75,neta,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,[搞不好对方也打算开群殴派对…？]
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.20,0:19:16.58,neta,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,[这个BGM明显是在恶搞Touch的同名第一期OP…]
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.29,0:19:39.34,neta,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,[中文读作：由于这神秘魔球括弧命名我的缘故]
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.03,0:19:51.05,neta,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,[这个时候对方应该学春日跳诅咒之舞削减阿虚（其实是长门…）的MP了…]
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.91,0:20:04.71,neta,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,[MP不足！]
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.96,0:20:19.08,neta,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,[「长门以厘米为单位，微微地对我点点头——」——没有表现出来！…吧？]
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.16,0:20:28.32,neta,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,[（虚：）「别把我概括在你们这些超乎常理的人当中啊」]
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.44,0:20:58.89,neta,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,[研究的成果就是女仆和管家…]
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.22,0:21:12.53,neta,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,[其实是“从异空间脱出用的那一招”的轻量版…\N总之就是阿虚给凉宫杀必死就对了。]
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.04,0:21:44.39,neta,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,[看来是讹了一笔…]


